</span> <span begin="57.651" end="57.930">like</span> <span begin="57.930" end="58.093">a</span> <span begin="58.137" end="58.520">bat</span><span begin="58.567" end="59.891">tle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每天都像一场战役</span></p><p begin="1:00.336" end="1:03.447" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.336" end="1:00.578">But</span> <span begin="1:00.578" end="1:00.839">eve</span><span begin="1:00.839" end="1:01.051">ry</span> <span begin="1:01.086" end="1:01.329">night</span> <span begin="1:01.329" end="1:01.580">with</span> <span begin="1:01.580" end="1:01.850">us</span> <span begin="1:01.850" end="1:02.080">is</span> <span begin="1:02.080" end="1:02.319">like</span> <span begin="1:02.319" end="1:02.488">a</span> <span begin="1:02.546" end="1:03.447">dream</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但每晚我们在一起都恍如梦境</span></p><p begin="1:03.526" end="1:05.249" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.526" end="1:03.785">Baby,</span> <span begin="1:03.785" end="1:03.911">we&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:03.911" end="1:04.044">the</span> <span begin="1:04.044" end="1:04.273">new</span> <span begin="1:04.273" end="1:04.466">ro</span><span begin="1:04.521" end="1:04.773">man</span><span begin="1:04.773" end="1:05.021">ti</span><span begin="1:05.021" end="1:05.249">cs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝 我们是新一代浪漫主义者</span></p><p begin="1:05.453" end="1:07.105" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.453" end="1:05.639">Come</span> <span begin="1:05.639" end="1:05.727">on,</span> <span begin="1:05.727" end="1:05.889">come</span> <span begin="1:05.889" end="1:06.252">along</span> <span begin="1:06.252" end="1:06.442">with</span> <span begin="1:06.498" end="1:07.105">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">来吧 与我并肩同行</span></p><p begin="1:07.205" end="1:08.959" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.205" end="1:07.496">Heart</span><span begin="1:07.496" end="1:07.704"